==English==

===Adjective===

# [[Suspend]]ed.
#: ''The hanging vines made the house look older than it was.''
# (''chess'') Vulnerable to capture.
#: ''Your queen rook is hanging.''

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[roikkuvat]] (1), [[altis]] (2)
