===Noun===

# The act of [[hang]]ing a person by the neck, generally until death.
# A public event in which a person is [[hang]]ed.
#:''The hanging of the bandits was attended by the whole village.''
# Anything wide, high and rather thin [[hang|hung]] as a [[decorative]] element (eg. curtains, gobelins, wallpaper,  posters, etc.)
# The way in which hangings are arranged
#:''I dislike the cramped hanging in the gallery of 18th century painters.''

